# WindKit

[![pipeline status](https://gitlab-internal.windenergy.dtu.dk/ram/software/pywasp/windkit/badges/master/pipeline.svg)](https://gitlab-internal.windenergy.dtu.dk/ram/software/pywasp/windkit/-/pipelines)
